<br /><br />

<h2>Strong with Click Handler</h2>
<Strong @onclick="HandleStrongClick" Class="btn btn-primary" Style="cursor: pointer; padding: 5px 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 3px;">
    Click me!
</Strong>

